alluxio.client.keyvalue

Class KeyValueMasterClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • alluxio.AbstractClient
      • alluxio.AbstractMasterClient
        • alluxio.client.keyvalue.KeyValueMasterClient
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    alluxio.Client, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    @ThreadSafe
public final class KeyValueMasterClient
extends alluxio.AbstractMasterClient
    A wrapper for the thrift client to interact with the key-value master, used by Alluxio clients. This wrapper provides thread safety, and retry mechanism.
